b276399a1771e56ad0fddbc192cce116ed0c164","tid":275833,"uid":1788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T13:03:35.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>邊有得大跌<br />\n樓價跌10% 已經大把人會走去接貨<br />\n<br />\n只有當世界出現經濟大崩盤<br />\n香港樓價先有機會大跌<br />\n過去廿年<br />\n97 07 都出現股災<br />\n而家等睇17會唔會又出現</blockquote><br />\n87都有，真係10年一次<br />\n<br />\n但對上呢十年已經變左好多，好依賴大陸資金。大陸市場對香港影響可能係最大。<br />\n<br />\n但係上面一有咩風吹草動就做野，鎖資金暴力救市，短期穩定翻個市場。<br />\n<br />\n除非上面真係暴力救市都失效，如果唔係佢地都好難下跌不止。<br />\n<br />\n講真，我又會想知如有世界大蕭條，香港今次會點。"},{"pid":"b336474aaaae3300f816dfd8d06e9950f9406e83","tid":275833,"uid":35221,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T13:04:58.000Z","msg":"係咪飲醉酒發up風"},{"pid":"912d8590b1f240d338b96af47a4004021b9059b0","tid":275833,"uid":51615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-08T13:04:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>2013年10月24日 <br />\n德銀睇樓市跌5成 <br />\n<a href=\"http://ps.hket.com/article/35564\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fps.hket.com%2Farticle%2F35564&d=9QbquKIHcXcapsTpPLjncgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=8b3748e0\" target=\"_blank\">http://ps.hket.com/article/35564</a> <br />\n<br />\n2014年5月29日 <br />\n德銀:樓市兩極化 維持樓價至少跌15%預測 <br />\n<a href=\"http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/stock/article/379410/%E5%BE%B7%E9%8A%80%3A%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%E5%85%A9%E6%A5%B5%E5%8C%96+%E7%B6%AD%E6%8C%81%E6%A8%93%E5%83%B9%E8%87%B3%E5%B0%91%E8%B7%8C15%25%E9%A0%90%E6%B8%AC\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww2.hkej.com%2Finstantnews%2Fstock%2Farticle%2F379410%2F%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E9%258A%2580%253A%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%25B8%2582%25E5%2585%25A9%25E6%25A5%25B5%25E5%258C%2596%2B%25E7%25B6%25AD%25E6%258C%2581%25E6%25A8%2593%25E5%2583%25B9%25E8%2587%25B3%25E5%25B0%2591%25E8%25B7%258C15%2525%25E9%25A0%2590%25E6%25B8%25AC&d=9QbquKIHcXcapsTpPLjncgdLCpCjoNGxXEizPMjNmRM%3D&h=c1218225\" target=\"_blank\">http://www2.hkej.com/instantnews/stock/article/379410/%E5%BE%B7%E9%8A%80%3A%E6%A8%93%E5%B8%82%E5%